00:18:17,597 --> 00:18:19,730
WHY DO YOU HAVE TO BE           
SUCH A JERK ALL THE TIME?       

447
00:18:19,732 --> 00:18:23,201
                THE TRUTH IS    
    I DON'T MEAN TO BE THIS WAY.

448
00:18:23,203 --> 00:18:26,537
              I-I JUST LASH OUT 
   BECAUSE OF MY LITTLE BROTHER.

449
00:18:26,539 --> 00:18:28,573
      [ INHALES SHARPLY, SIGHS ]

450
00:18:28,575 --> 00:18:31,609
                 HE'S SICK.     
        BEEN SICK ALL OUR LIVES.

451
00:18:31,611 --> 00:18:34,445
              SOMETIMES I THINK 
             IF I ACT REAL COOL 

452
00:18:34,447 --> 00:18:36,781
            AND NEVER LET ANYONE
                SEE MY PAIN,    

453
00:18:36,783 --> 00:18:39,083
             THEN MAYBE THE PAIN
                WILL GO AWAY.   

454
00:18:39,085 --> 00:18:42,620
            AND MAYBE I CAN TAKE
             HIS PAIN AWAY, TOO.

455
00:18:42,622 --> 00:18:45,123
KEVIN, I HAD NO IDEA.           

456
00:18:45,125 --> 00:18:46,657
                [ SNIFFLES ]    

457
00:18:46,659 --> 00:18:48,926
                 [ LAUGHS ]     

458
00:18:48,928 --> 00:18:52,063
                    DUDE!       
    I DON'T EVEN HAVE A BROTHER!

459
00:18:52,065 --> 00:18:54,499
   I'M LIKE THIS BECAUSE I THINK
                 IT'S FUNNY!    

460
00:18:54,501 --> 00:18:55,633
     [ GROWLS ]                 

461
00:18:55,635 --> 00:18:57,635
                  CHOWZERS.     

462
00:18:58,905 --> 00:18:59,704
       KEVIN!                   

463
00:19:02,976 --> 00:19:05,042
           [ GRUNTS ]           

464
00:19:07,981 --> 00:19:10,014
        WHAT'S HAPPENING?       

465
00:19:10,016 --> 00:19:11,949
            KEVIN...            

466
00:19:11,951 --> 00:19:13,151
            [ GASPS ]           

467
00:19:16,089 --> 00:19:17,488
             OH! NO!            

468
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:19,257
      WE<i> HAVE</i> TO BEAT HIM.      

469
00:19:19,259 --> 00:19:21,826
      HE DESERVES TO LOSE!      

470
00:19:23,463 --> 00:19:25,563
           [ SCREAMS ]          

471
00:19:26,699 --> 00:19:28,166
       [ CRICKETS CHIRP ]       

472
00:19:28,168 --> 00:19:29,267
     [ PANTING ]                

473
00:19:29,269 --> 00:19:30,434
   A-ARE YOU OKAY?              

474
00:19:30,436 --> 00:19:32,870
                 I THINK SO.    
                ARE<i> YOU</i> OKAY?   

475
00:19:32,872 --> 00:19:33,771
        YEAH.                   

476
00:19:33,773 --> 00:19:34,972
          [ BOTH SIGH ]         

477
00:19:34,974 --> 00:19:38,042
 SEEMS LIKE THE CAR             
    IS SAFE, TOO.               

478
00:19:41,648 --> 00:19:42,847
 WHAT ARE YOU DOING?            

479
00:19:42,849 --> 00:19:44,815
             WHAT ARE<i> WE</i> DOING? 

480
00:19:44,817 --> 00:19:46,117
WE'RE GETTING KEVIN BACK.       

481
00:19:46,119 --> 00:19:48,286
WE'RE ABOUT TO BEAT HIM         
  AT HIS OWN GAME!              

482
00:19:48,288 --> 00:19:52,523
        YEAH, BUT WHY DO WE EVEN
          HAVE TO PLAY HIS GAME?

483
00:19:52,525 --> 00:19:55,493
     BECAUSE --                 
   HE'S -- HE'S...              

484
00:19:55,495 --> 00:19:56,494
        DAGH!                   

485
00:19:56,496 --> 00:19:57,995
                   I KNOW!      

486
00:19:57,997 --> 00:20:01,399
    SO WHY SHOULD HE GET TO HAVE
       ANY SAY OVER HOW WE FEEL?

487
00:20:01,401 --> 00:20:02,667
     HE DOESN'T.                

488
00:20:02,669 --> 00:20:05,169
             BUT HE'S THE REASON
                WE'RE RACING.   

489
00:20:05,171 --> 00:20:08,706
                   STEVEN,      
       HE'S THE REASON WE FUSED.

490
00:20:08,708 --> 00:20:12,009
      [ GASPS ]                 
WE<i> ARE</i> OBSESSED WITH HIM.       

491
00:20:12,011 --> 00:20:15,079
              I WANT TO FINISH  
                THIS RACE...    

492
00:20:15,081 --> 00:20:16,581
              BUT NOT FOR HIM.  

493
00:20:16,583 --> 00:20:19,150
       RIGHT.                   

494
00:20:19,152 --> 00:20:21,819
       FOR US!                  

495
00:20:23,189 --> 00:20:24,855
    THE SUPREMO ISN'T MOVING!   

496
00:20:24,857 --> 00:20:26,357
               UGH, THAT'S IT.  

497
00:20:26,359 --> 00:20:28,226
 I'M GONNA GO UP THERE AND CHECK
              IF THEY'RE OKAY.  

498
00:20:28,228 --> 00:20:29,126
              WAIT!             

499
00:20:30,396 --> 00:20:32,396
         [ ENGINE REVS ]        

500
00:20:32,398 --> 00:20:34,298
        [ TIRES SQUEAL ]        

501
00:20:37,036 --> 00:20:39,337
                     ♪♪         

502
00:20:40,373 --> 00:20:41,973
            FINALLY.            

503
00:20:43,843 --> 00:20:45,076
         YOU CAUGHT UP.         

504
00:20:45,078 --> 00:20:47,411
    I WAS WORRIED YOU'D MISS    
         SEEING ME WIN.         

505
00:20:48,548 --> 00:20:51,082
    WHAT, SO YOU'RE SHY NOW?    

506
00:20:52,418 --> 00:20:54,151
              WHAT?             

507
00:20:59,726 --> 00:21:01,259
          Connie: WHOA.         

508
00:21:06,599 --> 00:21:08,599
           [ GIGGLES ]          

509
00:21:08,601 --> 00:21:10,968
           [ GROWLS ]           

510
00:21:21,047 --> 00:21:24,415
      AW! I WAS ROOTING FOR YOU,
                   DONDAI!      

511
00:21:24,417 --> 00:21:27,084
 KEVIN IS THE WORST!            
        BOO!                    

512
00:21:27,086 --> 00:21:29,620
                 WHAT, WHAT?    
                THAT'S RIGHT!   

513
00:21:29,622 --> 00:21:30,955
             FIRST PLACE, BABY! 

514
00:21:30,957 --> 00:21:33,157
                  IT'S LIKE     
             I INVENTED WINNING.

515
00:21:33,159 --> 00:21:34,458
     GOOD RACE.                 

516
00:21:35,295 --> 00:21:39,764
      YOU TRYING TO KISS MY HAND
    WITH YOUR HAND OR SOMETHING?

517
00:21:39,766 --> 00:21:42,066
  YOU KNOW, KEVIN,              
   YOU WERE RIGHT.              

518
00:21:42,068 --> 00:21:44,935
             [ SCOFFS ] I KNOW. 
                 ABOUT WHAT?    

519
00:21:44,937 --> 00:21:48,239
THE VIEW FROM THE MOUNTAIN      
 <i> WAS</i> PRETTY GREAT.             

520
00:21:48,241 --> 00:21:50,441
               HEY! DON'T TRY   
           TO TEACH<i> ME</i> A LESSON!

521
00:21:50,443 --> 00:21:51,909
                  YOU LOST!     

522
00:21:51,911 --> 00:21:54,278
  SECOND PLACE ISN'T SO BAD...  

523
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:57,481
        FOR MY FIRST TIME       
         DRIVING A CAR.         

524
00:21:57,483 --> 00:21:58,683
                 [ SCOFFS ]     

525
00:21:58,685 --> 00:22:00,184
                LOOK AT YOU.    

526
00:22:00,186 --> 00:22:02,153
     YOU'RE SO OBSESSED WITH ME,
        YOU'RE GONNA DRIVE AWAY.

527
00:22:02,155 --> 00:22:05,156
       FINE! GO PLAY WITH       
      SOME KIDDY TOY CARS!      

528
00:22:05,158 --> 00:22:07,024
 I COULD BEAT YOU AT THAT, TOO! 

529
00:22:07,026 --> 00:22:10,027
          DON'T FORGET,         
    YOU'RE OBSESSED WITH ME!    

530
00:22:10,029 --> 00:22:11,429
            OBSESSED!           

531
00:22:11,431 --> 00:22:14,999
        OBSEEEEEESSED!          

532
00:22:17,704 --> 00:22:18,936
       ♪ LOOK AT YOU GO ♪       

533
00:22:18,938 --> 00:22:20,638
      ♪ I JUST ADORE YOU ♪      

534
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:23,307
     ♪ I WISH THAT I KNEW ♪     

535
00:22:23,309 --> 00:22:30,014
     ♪ WHAT MAKES YOU THINK     
        I'M SO SPECIAL ♪        

